items.headline: The Amazing Everything Wiki-a wiki about, well, anything!
items.desc: Welcome to the Amazing Everything Wiki. Here, you'll find articles on just about anything! From electronic devices to Presidents of the United States to planets and more, if we have it, you'll find it. And that's exactly what we want each and every day at the Amazing Everything Wiki, now improved! It's bursting with creativity and wonder, so visit us now!

items.headline: Welcome to the Everything Wiki
items.desc: This wiki is simple. It is about mostly anything! You can post anything you want and read anything! You can add everything you can think of! Photos, videos, pages, forum posts, Anything! We even have custom badges for a lot of categories you can earn by editing a lot! I am looking for more GIFs to be added in the pictures category! Have fun! Please help the community grow!

items.headline: Dice: The Cube That Changes Everything
items.desc:
Dongtae often wondered if his life was completely messed up from the start.  He wished he was given the chance to change it into something better.  Then he was given that chance... with Dice.
Come visit the site and support a great Manhwa, it's got everything:  drama, suspense, mystery, love, and, of course, kick-ass fighting scenes.

items.headline: Learn on the All Everything Wiki!
items.desc: All Everything Wiki is about well... everything! So get on the All Everything Wiki and help us edit and make sure this wiki has EVERYTHING on it! Help us create pages, awesome things, and more! We even host contests! We are All Everything and we need you to be everything! C'mon down to the wiki! It will be worth it!

items.headline: The Everything Wiki
items.desc: This Wiki is simply about anything you may imagine! There are some useless things, some funny things, and some helpful things... Come and contribute to the Wiki, it would be very appreciated. Although this Wiki is a work in progress, you can still help make it better! If you see a link to a page that doesn't exist, be creative and make it yourself! There are unlimited possibilities that you can post and edit! I'll see you there!
